Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
get_metric_header(25.10)                              get_metric_header(25.10)

Name
       get_metric_header  -  Returns  the metric header information set by the
       set_metric_header command

Syntax
       get_metric_header

       -help

       [-id <db_id>]

       -name <header_name>

       Returns the metric header information set by the set_metric_header com-
       mand.

Parameters
       -id <db_id>
              Specifies the database ID.

              Data_type: string, optional

       -name <header> <_name >
              Specifies the name of the header.

              Data_type: string, required

       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each get_metric_header parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man get_metric_header

Example
       The following command sets the value bar of the metric header foo:

       > set_metric_header -name timing -value high

       The following command returns the header value of the metric header foo

       > get_metric_header -name timing

       high

